{"type":"message","id":"e317ce11","parentId":"97e6f822","timestamp":"2026-03-20T12:32:19.518Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Fri 2026-03-20 20:32 GMT+8] [Subagent Context] You are running as a subagent (depth 1/1). Results auto-announce to your requester; do not busy-poll for status.\n\n[Subagent Task]: 请帮我搜索以下4个领域的最新行业动态（2025-2026年）：\n\n1. 企业数字化转型\n2. 智能安防\n3. 网络系统集成\n4. IT运维服务\n\n每个领域搜索1-2条关键信息，重点关注：\n- 政策动态\n- 技术趋势\n- 市场需求变化\n- 头部企业动态\n\n请整理成3-5条关键信息，以适合道简网络（To B科技服务企业）决策参考的视角。"}],"timestamp":1774009939517}}
{"type":"message","id":"adf662b5","parentId":"e317ce11","timestamp":"2026-03-20T12:32:28.817Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户要求我搜索4个领域的最新行业动态（2025-2026年），每个领域1-2条关键信息，重点关注政策动态、技术趋势、市场需求变化、头部企业动态。然后整理成3-5条关键信息，以适合道简网络（To B科技服务企业）决策参考的视角。\n\n这是一个搜索任务，我需要使用miaoda-web-search skill来搜索相关信息。让我先读取这个skill的说明。","thinkingSignature":"adc3fa3a410d18602efdf1ee1b5e8327c7261b0f889b215b948f6bb35addacff"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ho5mdwz7nff0_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/workspace/agent/skills/miaoda-web-search/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":108,"output":128,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":30648,"totalTokens":30884,"cost":{"input":0.0000324,"output":0.0001536,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0.0036777599999999995,"total":0.0038637599999999995}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774009939518}}
{"type":"message","id":"83c920e6","parentId":"adf662b5","timestamp":"2026-03-20T12:32:28.825Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_ho5mdwz7nff0_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\r\nname: miaoda-web-search\r\ndescription: \"ALWAYS use this skill FIRST when you need to find, look up, or verify ANY information from the internet — do NOT guess URLs and fetch them directly. Provides necessary command usage instructions for keyword-based web search with AI-generated summaries. 触发词：搜索, 网页搜索, 搜一下, 查一下, 查询, 了解, 找一下, 帮我看看, web search, look up, find out, search, 搜索摘要, 查资料, 搜索引擎, 最新信息, 最近动态\"\r\noverride-tools:\r\n  - web_search\r\n---\r\n\r\n# Web Search\r\n\r\n通过 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary` 按关键词搜索互联网信息，由 AI 自动总结。\r\n\r\n## Quick Reference\r\n\r\n| 参数 | 说明 | 必需 | 默认值 |\r\n|------|------|------|--------|\r\n| `--query` | 搜索关键词（1-500 字符） | 是 | - |\r\n| `--output, -o` | 输出格式: text/json | 否 | text |\r\n\r\n## 命令选择决策树\r\n\r\n```\r\n用户想获取互联网信息\r\n├─ 有具体 URL → miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n├─ 无具体 URL，需搜索 → miaoda-studio-cli search-summary\r\n└─ 先搜索再深入 → search-summary 获取 URL → web-crawl 提取详情（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n```\r\n\r\n## 使用示例\r\n\r\n```bash\r\n# 按关键词搜索\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"React 19 新特性\"\r\n\r\n# 搜索并获取 JSON 输出\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"ByteDance 开源项目\" --output json\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Common Mistakes\r\n\r\n| 错误 | 正确做法 |\r\n|------|----------|\r\n| 无具体 URL 时用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl` | 无 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary`，有 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl`（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill） |\r\n| 搜索关键词超过 500 字符 | 提炼核心关键词，保持精简 |\r\n| 需要后续程序处理结果但未加 `--output json` | 需要解析结果时始终加 `--output json` |\r\n| 命令失败后不检查退出码 | 退出码 `1` 表示失败，检查参数和网络后重试 |\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774009948822}}
{"type":"message","id":"d5f6c860","parentId":"83c920e6","timestamp":"2026-03-20T12:32:35.716Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，我了解了如何使用web-search skill。现在我需要搜索4个领域的最新行业动态。让我为每个领域进行搜索。\n\n我需要搜索：\n1. 企业数字化转型 2025-2026 政策动态 技术趋势\n2. 智能安防 2025-2026 政策动态 技术趋势 市场趋势\n3. 网络系统集成 2025-2026 市场趋势 技术趋势\n4. IT运维服务 2025-2026 市场需求 头部企业\n\n让我分别搜索这4个领域的信息。","thinkingSignature":"7740eea8aa2f69362fd21bfb9884bd41beb0db85943cb574cd4eddeec6a16f7a"},{"type":"text","text":"我来搜索这4个领域的最新行业动态。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_sbzszztjsuvc_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"企业数字化转型 2025 2026 政策动态 技术趋势 头部企业\" --output json"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_sbzszztjsuvc_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"智能安防 2025 2026 技术趋势 市场需求 政策\" --output json"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_sbzszztjsuvc_3","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"网络系统集成 2025 2026 市场趋势 技术发展\" --output json"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_sbzszztjsuvc_4","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"IT运维服务 2025 2026 市场需求 头部企业 智能化\" --output json"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":914,"output":312,"cacheRead":30485,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":31711,"cost":{"input":0.0002742,"output":0.0003744,"cacheRead":0.0009145499999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00156315}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774009948825}}
